opinions.text:
ORDER
The defendant’s motion to affirm the judgment of the Superior Court pursuant to Rule 16(g) is granted.
DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Ralph R. Ryan, Pawtucket, for plaintiff.
Carroll, McHugh & Pirraglia, John G. Carroll, Providence, for defendant.
